    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">View</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">View toolbar and menu</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="T_Menu">View toolbar</text> is <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">below</text> the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic area</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">View menu</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><image src="MD-Menu-View2.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt;" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[View menu]]></caption></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">View toolbar</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="T_Menu">View toolbar</text> is <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">BELOW</text> the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><image src="MD-TOOLBARS-VIEW.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[View toolbar]]></caption></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><anchor id="ViewToolbaricons"><keywords><keyword>View toolbar<keyword>icons</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor>View toolbar icons</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="9" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Toolbar-View-StandardViews.ipp" scale="-99.90%" figurelistinclude="0"></image>&#32;</para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Front ; Back ; Left ; Right ; Top ; Bottom</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">Front-View</text> is the <text styleclass="VariableName">XY-Plane</text> of the <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">active</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">TOP-TIP: &#160;Clipped Models </text>- if part of the model does not display correctly in the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>, it is a <text styleclass="VariableName">Clipped-Model</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT">. </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Models of very large machines, e.g. Large Rotary Machines, can become </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT">clipped.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">If the model is clipped:</para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Click <text styleclass="T_Menu">Front-View</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click</text><text styleclass="T_Menu"> Zoom-Extents</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:1px; background-color:#c0c0c0;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Icon-View-AlignAxes.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">View Align:</text></para>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Interface">Part-Editor</text> : Click <text styleclass="T_Menu">View Align</text> to make horizontal the <text styleclass="Interface">X–axis</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor :</text>&#32;<text styleclass="T_Menu">Click View</text> Align to make horizontal the <text styleclass="Interface">X–axis</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Base-Part</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:1px; background-color:#c0c0c0;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Icon-View-NormalTo.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="T_Menu">View Normal to a Plane</para>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">To make the view normal(<text style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;;">⊥</text>) to a <text styleclass="Element">Plane</text>:</para>
          <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click <text styleclass="T_Menu">View Normal to Plane</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Plane" styleclass="Element">Plane</link></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click <image src="OK-tiny-13-17.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Command-Manager" styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</link></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="background-color:#c0c0c0;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Icon-View-Spin.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">SPIN - Smooth (Shortcut : SHIFT+DRAG)</text></para>
          <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="VariableName">SHIFT+Drag</text> to rotate the model at your mouse position, approximately.<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">SPIN - about a Point </text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text style="font-weight:normal;">Click F3, to view the FRONT View</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text style="font-weight:normal;">Click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">or move your mouse-pointer to locate the center of the Spin-axis</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="T_Menu">SHIFT+Drag</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">to spin the model about the </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">, and not the Origin</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Bullets">&#32;<text styleclass="T_Menu">SPIN - increments:</text></para>
          <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Press any of these keys or key-combinations on your keyboard<text styleclass="VariableName">: </text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="6" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">10º Spin-Increments: &#160;LEFT / RIGHT &amp; UP / DOWN arrow-keys</li>
          </list>
          <list id="7" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">30º Spin-Increments: &#160;CTRL + LEFT / RIGHT &amp; UP / DOWN arrow-keys </li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">90º Spin-Increments: &#160;SHIFT + LEFT / RIGHT &amp; UP / DOWN arrows-keys</li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="vertical-align:top; width:1px; background-color:#c0c0c0;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Icon-View-Pan.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">PAN: &#160;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Drag to move the model with your mouse-pointer.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Shortcut: CTRL + Drag</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">CTRL+Drag</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">, and wait for your model to move if the model is a large, then continue to CTRL+Drag.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:1px; background-color:#c0c0c0;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Icon-View-ZoomExtents.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Zoom Extents : </text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;">To </text><text styleclass="Body Text">display the complete model.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Use </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Zoom extents</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to see all of the model. Also use </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Zoom extents</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> if the model is clipping.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
