        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Zoom In </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">SHORTCUT: Mouse-Scroll-Wheel: Zoom in/out at your mouse position.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:1px; background-color:#c0c0c0;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Icon-View-ZoomOut.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
