          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">&#32;</text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Zoom Out </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">SHORTCUT: Mouse-Scroll-Wheel: Zoom in/out at your mouse position.</para>
        </td>
